Templated Html helpers

Used for data display and input
It generate HTML automatically as per model

Calendar from date
Number from int
checkbox from bool etc.
Can generate a HTML for complete model with a single tag

types of Templated html helpers

Display
	@Html.Display() : Used to display value with some extra functionality
	@Html.DisplayFor() : Strongly binding version of last helpers
	@Html.DisplayName() : Used to display only the name of property
	@Html.DisplayNameFor() : Strongly binding version of last helpers
	@Html.DisplayText() : Used to display only the value of model property
	@Html.DisplayTextFor() : Strongly binding version of last helpers
	@Html.DisplayForModel() : Used to display complete model data

Edit/input
	@Html.Editor()
	@Html.EditorFor()
	@Html.EditorForModel()

